↑ citocinas/ quimocinas en sangre","guid":"FyuIKGGUMrsnymWEI7qqSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"43","text":"- Mecanismo","guid":"IOO6fLKKLd36q7ROhHG-0Q","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"- TNF-α, IL-2, IL-1β, IL-6 → ↑ síntesis ferritina vía FER2 y NF-κB","guid":"Ad7xlZoDNyvbIwxyfUXXBQ","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"- Infiltración histiocítica linfática en bazo, ganglios, médula","guid":"F3cTYs9ONWxNlxrY6hD14Q","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"- Hemoglobina-haptoglobina → ↑ ferritina (↑ respuesta antioxidante)","guid":"GIyd5ZRD6fMnpIDRduPCHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"43","text":"- Patogenia común","guid":"rYFD6bDGBItQvLwYlHl5Eg","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"- Perfiles citocinéticos y vías de señalización similares","guid":"USzlsK_eCeY0lqoQZtTCFA","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"- Mediada por liberación IFN-γ, IL-2 por CTLs → activación JAKs, STATs, NF-κB en macrófagos","guid":"OsAlf9C3I-7xrzCO3b19nA","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"43","text":"- Consecuencias","guid":"ZuQGa72a61ekpaj4j2nxRg","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"- IFN-γ y TNF-α implicados en pancytopenia","guid":"gnYI1GCXLM9knDiPHT5vVw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"- TNF-α relacionado con hipertrigliceridemia","guid":"3dQh7rXcoBm5xPK1B2vshA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"- Disfunción hepática → coagulopatía","guid":"xFA1NX1aeiw7IyAaaCvGOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"43","text":"- Tratamiento","guid":"IZkX7Evnnk3RcmbaGozLxg","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- Antibióticos/antivirales para etiologías infecciosas","guid":"Sybl-9HGTiFByl01YA0iZA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Antiinflamatorios: esteroides,\\Nciclosporina, etoposide, biológicos","guid":"9VKm6iptau75ULo3kV1OZg","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"- Glucocorticoides (30 mg/kg/d máx. 1 g/día) →\\Ncalcineurina (2-7 mg/kg/día) → etoposide/biológicos","guid":"9LCuf_CAXKaDuwJgHZl8GQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"- Efectos adversos esteroides: obesidad, osteoporosis,\\Nretardo crecimiento, complicaciones infecciosas","guid":"v2k0nLsAkc6EQZhR4FGLeg","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"- Uso off-label de biológicos en enfermedad refractaria (IL-1, IL-6, TNF-α, IFN-γ, CTLA-4, CD20, JAK1/2)","guid":"T4OE9MOBSH7bG3ALQqAMPA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"43","text":"- Conclusión","guid":"LCoaPljJ062NIeZWhx2SDg","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"- Revisión de mecanismos inmunopatológicos de sHLH/MAS","guid":"lcNBsz7_PbpL_g-mu8v7Mw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"- Identificación de moléculas y vías señalización como blancos terapéuticos","guid":"eH16Be2ZFpcOQbYA4P692w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"40","text":"- Defectos en células NK y\\NCTL en sHLH/MAS","guid":"9exfLgpFTvBOhopVuoAmQQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"- Mecanismo primario: fallo de células NK y CTL → proliferación descontrolada de células inmunes → ↑ citocinas","guid":"rXJWhqtXS4zonAbhU3d-SA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"- Células NK y CTL eliminan\\Ncélulas anormales mediante:","guid":"Hj5mE1_eNfMOR2EZZUjUEw","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"1. Liberación de gránulos líticos (lisosomas, perforina, granzimas)","guid":"WwcElZ-q2emTEhI6LxAs7Q","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"2. Inducción de apoptosis (ligando TRAIL/Fas)","guid":"x1KoHd7wYfJ0jg6chPH83Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"70","text":"- Consecuencias","guid":"i7sWBQyXdZrkDIHnihUaog","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"- Falla en mecanismos → proliferación inmunológica y bucle inflamatorio persistente","guid":"54bB8Pkfh9HqZVOdidqkEg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"- Enfermedad de Kawasaki y MAS","guid":"7hzGpQFn9DU4CDCX_oO9yQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"- CTLs en arteria coronaria sin perforina/granzima → defecto en NKG2A","guid":"lZb_A0bDo_TOUHQYH9vOsA","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"- Células\\NNK","guid":"FMUhxH60Y9Wt3k120HJiaQ","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"- CD56dim (citotóxicas, ↑ perforina, ↓ citocinas)","guid":"UZhxMWYxQULpiXK8aCydMA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"- CD56bright (↑ citocinas, pobre efecto citotóxico)","guid":"M8RIQLud7tpWZpDZ8dDnWg","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"- En sJIA/MAS: ↓ CD56bright, ↓ actividad citotóxica CD56dim","guid":"Y6twIMwqF5kg82bF4oZmBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"75","text":"- fHLH","guid":"2HhjKFKVGsCUjoLZL1jf3w","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- Mutaciones en genes de citotoxicidad granular (PRF1, UNC13D, etc.)","guid":"5YF0SA3i8WyR1qCor5Tt1A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"70","text":"- Terapéuticas","guid":"7kEimjBQdM2G8j0PAB5RTA","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- Etopósido: induce apoptosis en células T, ↓ IFN-γ","guid":"h8F8IL62lafDMstIhn9dKg","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- Alemtuzumab: depleta células T maduras","guid":"QyxPT_f-KYC1_oRmDKnZ6Q","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"- Ciclosporina: inhibe actividad células T","guid":"FzVIofKBShanl0GTmTAVOw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"- Emapalumab: anticuerpo\\Nbloqueante anti-IFN-γ","guid":"T6467FKMk6WycW3W69LyDQ","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"- IFN-γ clave en patogénesis, promueve\\Nliberación citocinas proinflamatorias","guid":"qtaowkw7nB1JHaPye5-vuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"- IL-18","guid":"wLNWpbekyxUtsRHhKLwvBA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"- Correlación con actividad de sJIA, induce muerte células NK","guid":"uUSecnkOdPwkKYUt3Dv2Jw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"- Uso de IL-18BP o anticuerpo neutralizante anti-IL-18","guid":"nZTRJn7KI1Jp_DwEZFwNmQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"85","text":"- Daclizumab","guid":"8DgiGX2Zp5EUafzJ2N7bCQ","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"- Anticuerpo anti-IL-2Rα, regula células T y NK, efectivo en MS y fHLH","guid":"PMeyJToTEeW5NFmj8vGeNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"85","text":"- Potenciales blancos\\Nterapéuticos","guid":"JmQn5Gyr-yvxVqQE1ISJ-w","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"- Bloqueo de receptores inhibidores en células NK (KIR, NKG2A)","guid":"ujdC4fDGFODBxfGJ5PKt4g","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"- Monalizumab y anticuerpos contra KIR para restaurar citotoxicidad NK","guid":"zIiLRSDwqBC9se1VAKFiIw","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"- Activación excesiva de CTLs\\Npor infección en sHLH/MAS","guid":"oFguOkHVeGSNwzuqALLPTA","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"- Infecciones desencadenantes: EBV, herpesvirus, Leishmania, virus influenza, VIH, SARS-CoV-2","guid":"oKAFrqen2vFO3hQD6q3oqQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"- Infección → activación inmunidad\\Ninnata → proliferación CTLs","guid":"XgmuNqHohpJofbgmAzMGhQ","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"- Marcadores CTLs activados: ↑ CD25, PD1, CD95","guid":"6fcpTX8urPdygEDqZv-tVA","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"- En sHLH: ↑ CTLs activados CD38high/HLADR+","guid":"KEoZLeQ9KL6ge4H4a8kmxg","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"99","text":"- Laboratorio: correlación entre ferritina, hemoglobina, LDH y CTLs CD38high/HLADR+","guid":"ds3OIEYdkslp24N_QRDlbA","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"99","text":"- EBV y sHLH/MAS","guid":"Mlwm9Ui2EW9vwSvZjjlRiA","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- EBV infecta células B, NK, T → sHLH/MAS fulminante","guid":"Tz0Q3UHRAz__0XHY3HSUpQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"99","text":"- Síntomas: fiebre, hepatosplenomegalia, linfadenopatía, linfocitosis atípica","guid":"JqMlGevFMl5GplPuqn4xsQ","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"99","text":"- Tratamiento: IVIG, rituximab (anti-CD20)","guid":"dlxAQvMs8zWc1EpbZER7ZA","children":[]},{"id":