":"120","text":"- Receptores inmunológicos en\\Nmacrófagos:","guid":"81ysL8Ha6kkGlmJHQkUP2Q","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"- TLRs: respuesta inmune innata","guid":"4P8OWgPO7J5q8IDnVKvnIQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"- FcRs: respuesta inmune adaptativa","guid":"5aqWFuZlnTrZEUikw7_x3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"120","text":"- Señalización TLR:","guid":"d9x4OwWCmOsmLEKmZ4QcUQ","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- Moléculas: MyD88,\\NTIRAP, TRAF6","guid":"287yVtFIASYN0MPMZ3N8mg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"- Factores\\Ntranscripción: NF-κB,\\NAP-1","guid":"Y3wIMgdl86Mrvp0kEbD9dQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"120","text":"- Activación FcR:","guid":"kc9uIXvs7Kw3D-L3IAwhmQ","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"- Fosforilación ITAMs → activa PLC, flujo\\Ncalcio, producción NADPH","guid":"uqJVwnQXdh0Uw2r61E-QUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"120","text":"- TLR + FcR:","guid":"Dkh-Nl_EhERFbWOtq3e41w","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"- Controla síntesis citocinas →\\Nrespuesta inmune inflamatoria","guid":"WNOQKd7sM9vZq8Mt_wnaPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"120","text":"- Etapas\\Ntempranas:","guid":"5gclqHjsH6j35wx5O4-U2A","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"- DAMPs activan TLRs","guid":"B_O1i1aay62rxjLLHEgb0A","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"- Baja IgG → activación fuerte TLR (vía MyD88)\\Npero débil FcR (vía Syk)","guid":"ohKJ0hG1jFonr69v_hKRxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"120","text":"- Opsonización\\Ncon IgG:","guid":"czEIkQIWVLkOgFOAcJ43pA","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"- ↑ sinergia TLR–FcR → polarización proinflamatoria (↑ TNF-α, IL-8, IL-1β)","guid":"j5RmkUOHjJH3LQUj3dnsVQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"- Reclutamiento neutrófilos, expresión TLRs + FcRIs en basófilos/mastocitos","guid":"hCZ7aD-w8CuK-gw3_Wwn-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"120","text":"- Trastornos autoinmunes\\N(ej. LES) y sHLH/MAS:","guid":"O970JIlij2_WiXiIBWVRbA","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"- Autoanticuerpos/complejos inmunes →\\Nrespuesta inflamatoria en macrófagos","guid":"2rIPMXzKXtX6KZNohEghcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"120","text":"- Terapia:","guid":"ozQhxFtCPqZGBtjtlLcmMw","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"- Esteroides dosis alta","guid":"9agWca6JH-v3DUikXYGiOw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"- Resistencia a esteroides →\\Nanticuerpo anti-FcRIII, IVIG","guid":"hgSVx-JfQFqucpJ0P_1WBw","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"- IVIG induce expresión FcRIIB en macrófagos, previene inflamación autoanticuerpos","guid":"nFxEfzdiBFNQ-xnmozgiVw","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"- Bloqueo FcRIIA en monocitos/macrófagos → ↓ secreción TNF-α","guid":"Xyxm-A3DWQOwOAme_6T1MA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"120","text":"- Investigación:","guid":"UExZDDX-xG12zQa0EvmyLQ","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"- Efectos TLR–FcR\\Ncoactivación poco\\Nexplorados","guid":"Ie1jK2avuCJBcmC5mGZn3Q","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"- Modificación de balsas lipídicas\\Nafecta señalización IL-6 y\\Nfagocitosis FcR-mediada","guid":"FXVsP2ey4JQXAicRp6-X8Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"- Asociación de sHLH/MAS con\\Nmalignidad y terapia CAR","guid":"i0NvDbkeBj3QFzqDPbydZA","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"- Cánceres linfoides y terapias CAR (CAR-T, CAR-NK, CAR-macrofago) →\\N↑ incidencia sHLH (hasta 46%)","guid":"VcpLTRKa_n1kBIeWB8-XOA","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"- Terapia anti-CD19 CAR-T →\\NsHLH/MAS como toxicidad","guid":"3ihevORrAKVPnPKY_OwnXg","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"- Patrones HLH observados tras\\Nterapia anti-CD22 CAR-T","guid":"yaoEdsILVnLNzhuXi8FGcA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"- Terapia CAR: reconocimiento de antígenos → liberación masiva de\\Nperforina, granzimas, citocinas → piropoptosis en células cancerígenas","guid":"4BTuLJFcw-FbYmQhdZcjdA","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"- Comparación:","guid":"fnbjUfohaWPQ8MbK3eSDbA","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"- CAR-T: ↑ perforina, gasdermina → ↑ daño celular","guid":"UBDhS02jRQosc-0uZe26pQ","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"- CTLs: liberación menor perforina/granzimas → reparación membrana","guid":"ALOWhoIeLxWBrYWXoKDkJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"148","text":"- Productos proinflamatorios (DAMPs, ATP, dsDNA, RNA, histonas)\\Nactivan CTLs y macrófagos → sHLH/MAS","guid":"ElfksrfvKCFxo1336TZSDg","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"148","text":"- sHLH/MAS en terapia CAR → niveles extremos de ferritina","guid":"XZw6wXkmmvfAynq8z76VGQ","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"148","text":"- Tratamiento recomendado\\Npara sHLH/MAS","guid":"rWuqdY1hZFZG8RDvrSgE9w","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"- Corticosteroides\\N+/- biológicos","guid":"EyRc7ypmlL8iseiLA2-Lww","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"- Línea de tratamiento: anakinra, ruxolitinib, emapalumab","guid":"XS3JAW6fbFN2NA_aZF0rNw","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"- Uso de tocilizumab (TCZ) por su relación con IL-6","guid":"hXRiWxE76O820g6otN95-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"- Combinación anakinra + TCZ en práctica clínica","guid":"nBaq8x_J9EB290eJkCXNgg","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"- Liberación de IL-1 precede a IL-6 → posible iniciación de CRS por IL-1","guid":"Xjdsc612V3pBXiva-pYYlA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"158","text":"- Necesidad de más estudios randomizados\\Npara evaluar eficacia y seguridad de TCZ","guid":"tyW9PI4_MOC7PrC2NQzv-w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"0","text":"- Conclusión y\\Nperspectivas sobre\\NsHLH/MAS","guid":"1HyuPH1TDAecYVdNu-wqXw","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"- Retos:","guid":"BDqqCHKYdnSRuEbyryZJbA","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"- Diagnóstico basado\\Nen biomarcadores","guid":"nS15ZvrQzOQClfWJboteZw","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"- Terapias dirigidasr","guid":"RZfmUNdyqcuzIYX9dCwk0Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"- Propuestas:","guid":"LoIOlferzJ-fFxdtCCKnlw","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"- Algoritmos de IA integrando etiología, perfiles\\Ncitocínicos, parámetros bioquímicos/clínicos","guid":"R6FPoqq2f1roQwlklxRaUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"165","text":"- Limitaciones:","guid":"4-4bep6Jb0XbM73QYwxU2A","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"- Informática en tiempo real no viable actualmente","guid":"faClzU9qYxBs77TyIW3GYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"165","text":"- Estrategia\\Nterapéutica:","guid":"CYYXz-xiERpx00tw3b5MkA","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"- Biológicos inhiben producción/liberación de\\Ncitocinas proinflamatorias","guid":"B8h4Pe1r0dRSZvw5pqhnLA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"- Combinación biológicos + inmunosupresores → ↑ efectividad","guid":"iFh-CJeAn0yvlEpmddmR8g","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"- Medicina de precisión necesaria debido\\Na variabilidad actividad citocínica","guid":"LqchfL26-zgrnJycohglQw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"- Monoterapia citocínica puede ser inefectiva →\\Nposible dyshomeostasis de redes citocínicas","guid":"aaTncRKBqQ24MpVhxNHTRw","children":[]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"165","text":"- Enfoque\\Nfarmacológico\\Npotencial:","guid":"WG5pSnXcuYQrohSnXx-oog","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"- Dirigirse a desencadenantes upstream de tormenta de citocinas","guid":"y3GpicIOaI6g7OL_biB1KQ","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"- Reducir severidad inflamatoria sin alterar red de citocinas","guid":"PEd3HergTxrkJJVPIdDGAA","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"165","text":"- Investigación y\\Ndesarrollo:","guid":"yHKqaMLVrmdO4Kf9phD3MA","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"- Estrategias diagnósticas y tratamientos evolucionan continuamente","guid":"5WQ_fQdxnNEszUNChBHs7g","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"- Investigación patológica y traslacional sistemática esencial","guid":"KFAznMepgpp-N-PuyJMIew","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"- Estudios retrospectivos y controlados bajo condiciones específicas","guid":"GulM1hIKv6Q5ZgsP2AGZ7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"165","text":"- Futuro:","guid":"CHRfC7STkwf08RX6gfdUzg","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"- Perspectivas y soluciones para medicina de precisión en sHLH/MAS","guid":"e-EsdqhgMLttWE6xYos6xA","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":186,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Linfohistocitosis hemofagocitica-2024","id":"map_802","resolved_references":[]}